      {
         "id": "SECTION_andes",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "<p><h3>Andean numerical systems</h3><h4>Quipus</h4>The quipu system is an ancient method of counting, likely originating in the sacred city of Caral, Peru (<htcite0> ; <htcite1> ; <htcite2>):</p><p class=\"desc\"><img id=\"imgQuipuPanel\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgQuipuPanel', '0%')\" class=\"imgcenter\"/><b>Figure 2</b>: Panel at the Caral archaeological site, © ZonaArqueólogicaCaral (<htcite3> ; <htcite4>). Photo taken on <htdate5>, during a visit to the archaeological site of Caral.</p>",
               "source": [
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "720f6dfd-4b86-4e07-a887-1010e1041a4d",
                     "text": "Ruta Caral",
                     "page": "",
                     "date_time": {
                        "type": "gregory",
                        "year": "2024",
                        "month": "11",
                        "day": "02"
                     }
                  },
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "03c3743c-d268-4730-ba8e-d36b5c49e781",
                     "text": "Youtube - Caral Perú Oficial",
                     "page": "",
                     "date_time": {
                        "type": "gregory",
                        "year": "2024",
                        "month": "11",
                        "day": "02"
                     }
                  },
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "a7abe0b7-b3bf-44d6-ab4d-e7d32d2586ad",
                     "text": "Moras, Roberto.",
                     "page": "",
                     "date_time": {
                        "type": "gregory",
                        "year": "2024",
                        "month": "11",
                        "day": "02"
                     }
                  },
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "720f6dfd-4b86-4e07-a887-1010e1041a4d",
                     "text": "Ruta Caral",
                     "page": "",
                     "date_time": {
                        "type": "gregory",
                        "year": "2024",
                        "month": "11",
                        "day": "02"
                     }
                  },
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "03c3743c-d268-4730-ba8e-d36b5c49e781",
                     "text": "Youtube - Caral Perú Oficial",
                     "page": "",
